message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and machine learning techniques for audio and music data. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis, which can be applied to music emotion recognition. cs.LG is another possible category as it deals with machine learning techniques, which are used in the proposed method. cs.AI and cs.CV are less likely categories as they deal with artificial intelligence and computer vision respectively, which are not directly related to music emotion recognition.
